public class ListDownloaderThread
extends javax.swing.SwingWorker<java.lang.Object,java.lang.String>

A SwingWorker thread that downloads ReMix list pages.

These are the HTML files displayed to a visitor of ocremix.org looking at the "View All ReMixes in descending chronological order" page.
